=== 直升機 ===
[[File:Mi-35_Hind_Akbar.jpg|thumb]]武裝直升機.]]
[[File:Indian_air_force_dhruv_helicopter_j4042_arp.jpg|thumb]]]]
北極星直升機是印度空軍一種輕型直升機，除了用作運輸及各種雜務，新式的型號亦會充當攻擊直升機<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Dhruv/|title=HAL Dhruv|accessdate=2010-07-20|quote=IAF Dhruvs, can carry a 20mm gun plus eight anti-tank guided missiles (ATGMs) or four air-to-air missiles or four 68mm rocket pods on outriggers.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100330153328/http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Dhruv|archivedate=2010年3月30日}}</ref>，並遂步取代主要用作訓練、拯救及運輸用的雲雀III型直升機<ref name="Chetak">{{cite web|url=http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Chetak/|title=HAL Chetak (Alouette III)|accessdate=2010-07-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100207181106/http://bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Chetak/|archivedate=2010年2月7日}}</ref>。印度豹直升機就適合高海拔行動，一般用於運輸及搜救任務<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Cheetah/|title=HAL Cheetah (Alouette II)|accessdate=2010-07-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100329175152/http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Cheetah|archivedate=2010年3月29日}}</ref>。[[Mi-8直升機|Mi-8直升機]]及[[Mi-17直昇機|Mi-17直昇機]]則是印度空軍的中型直升機，Mi-17正在逐步取代Mi-8<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Mi8/ |title=Mil Mi-8 (Hip) Rana |accessdate=2010-07-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100330151244/http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Mi8 |archivedate=2010年3月30日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Mi17/ |title=Mil Mi-17 (Hip) Pratap |accessdate=2010-07-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100421025030/http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Mi17/ |archivedate=2010年4月21日 }}</ref>。印度空軍已訂購了兩批分別80架及59架的新式Mi-17V-5直升機以取代現有的兩款米系列中型直升機<ref name="Mi-17">{{cite web|url=http://www.indiastrategic.in/topstories694.htm|title=Russia continues to dominate Indian military aviation|author=Gulshan Luthra and Air Marshal Ashok Goel (Retd)|publisher=India Strategic|date=August 2010|accessdate=2010-08-20|archive-date=2010-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100822022445/http://indiastrategic.in/topstories694.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印度空軍現在也有4架[[Mi-26直升機|Mi-26直升機]]這種重型直升機，它可以用來運輸部隊及緊急運送傷員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Mi26/|title=Mil Mi-26 (Halo)|accessdate=2010-07-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100329153008/http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Mi26|archivedate=2010年3月29日}}</ref>。Mi-35直升機則主力用作攻擊直升機，也可運輸少量士兵，現有兩架服役<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Mi25/|title=Mil Mi-25 / Mi-35 (Hind) Akbar|accessdate=2010-07-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100329125300/http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Images/Current/Helicopters/Mi25|archivedate=2010年3月29日}}</ref>。

