二十世紀九十年代末，因為飛機退役及意外事故，印度空軍的戰力減少了，故此印度空軍為現有機隊、裝備及設施進行升級，並購置印度本土及外地的新式的飛機及裝備。隨著這些措施讓空軍飛機數量回升，印度空軍就計劃在2022年擴展至42個中隊<ref name="42 Squad">{{cite news| title=IAF fighter squadrons to rise to 42 by 2022: Antony| url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/IAF_fighter_squadrons_to_rise_to_42_by_2022_Antony/articleshow/4151093.cms| work=The Times of India| date=2009-02-18| accessdate=2009-04-24| archive-date=2009-02-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090221161515/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/IAF_fighter_squadrons_to_rise_to_42_by_2022_Antony/articleshow/4151093.cms| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

